  "body": "Currently buidler network need to be provided a set of private key with balances.\r\nFor cases where we want to have the buidlerevm run with a mnemonic based accounts (like when running `buidler node` with a test metamask account, we need to convert such mnemonic into private keys in the buidlerc.config first\r\n\r\nI suggest the following types to allow passing a mnemonic for buidlerevm network too\r\n```\r\nexport interface BuidlerNetworkConfig extends CommonNetworkConfig {\r\n  accounts?: BuidlerNetworkAccount[] | BuidlerNetworkHDAccountsConfig;\r\n  ...\r\n}\r\n\r\nexport interface BuidlerNetworkHDAccountsConfig extends HDAccountsConfig {\r\n  balance: string;\r\n}\r\n```",
